snippet.title: Nihil Ignis Incident 48 - VHS Urbex Found Footage "Incident" Series - Tape 4 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now for 2.99$! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/nihil-ignis-incident-48

Trailer for the fourth and final installment in the "Incident" tape series. 

Description: Nihil Ignis Incident 48 is a realistic urban exploration VHS  Found Footage horror title.

Story: The year is 1991, you are a urban explorer on a mission tonight to investigate a long abandoned 1940s fire station named Nihil ignis. Supposedly the premise was shutdown in 1948, and has been abandoned now for 43 years. Document the premise and unfold its past through your camera.

VHS Urbex Found Footage "Incident" Tape Series - 4 titles:

    Grainwind Incident 77 - Free https://azagamestudio.itch.io/grainwi...
    Sanevol Incident 44 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/grainwi...
    Lakelight Elementary Incident 68 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/lakelig...
    Nihil Ignis Incident 48 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/nihil-i...
